            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "This is definitely missing `volatile`.\n\nI'm a bit suspicious of this solution in general because I think the list is incomplete (and I don't think `volatile` makes it complete).\n\nI think it'd be better to be more selective about loading the `view` submodule only when `view` is specifically looked. I don't know how hard that is though.",
            "commit_id": "1565b7571e3daf5ae9778bb2fa5b07bf7a6062bf",
            "created_at": "2026-02-03T21:55:02Z",
            "diff_hunk": "@@ -6,6 +6,7 @@\n from . import MemoryView\n from .StringEncoding import EncodedString\n \n+NON_TYPE_NAMES = {'pointer', 'const'}",
